248
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:47,326
Toilet. Peeing. Pooping.

249
00:17:48,300 --> 00:17:51,213
The toilet. The toilet!

250
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:57,360
Tim?

251
00:18:00,406 --> 00:18:03,426
Help. I was searching for fashion heaven.

252
00:18:05,463 --> 00:18:06,886
I need to go to the toilet.

253
00:18:11,446 --> 00:18:13,153
Small stinky or big stinky?

254
00:18:16,393 --> 00:18:17,553
Very big stinky.

255
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,960
I'm tired. I'll go sleep in the gym hall.

256
00:18:23,173 --> 00:18:24,500
<i>TOILETS | GYM HALL</i>

257
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,353
So...

258
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:27,466
Will you help me?

259
00:18:35,470 --> 00:18:36,453
Come with me.

260
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,206
Hello?

261
00:19:02,633 --> 00:19:03,753
Hey!

262
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,313
Mr Hulst?

263
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:12,093
What are those clothes?

264
00:19:12,202 --> 00:19:13,346
Isn't it beautiful?

265
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:16,853
I found it in fashion heaven.

266
00:19:17,766 --> 00:19:19,699
So it does exist?

267
00:19:19,923 --> 00:19:20,980
Yeah.

268
00:19:21,897 --> 00:19:23,133
But where is it?

269
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:28,946
No other student has ever been
close to it as often as you.

270
00:19:34,203 --> 00:19:37,546
Come on, Eric. Keep your head up.

271
00:20:06,149 --> 00:20:08,369
Hallelujah!

272
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:15,206
I'm sorry, Armani. I need to
send you away. You ate something.

273
00:20:16,423 --> 00:20:17,973
What I don't get, though...

274
00:20:18,450 --> 00:20:20,026
