275
00:20:20,333 --> 00:20:23,306
You just want to eat something.
But why eat shit?

276
00:20:24,139 --> 00:20:25,100
You see...

277
00:20:27,419 --> 00:20:30,233
It was Eddy...
- I don't want to hear it.

278
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:32,439
So you didn't blow him?

279
00:20:32,812 --> 00:20:33,726
No.

280
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,220
Armani talks shit.

281
00:20:39,387 --> 00:20:41,373
But you two are... dating?

282
00:20:42,023 --> 00:20:42,946
Yeah.

283
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:48,013
<i>Life goes on</i>, Tim.

284
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:51,253
And I love you too. So very much.

285
00:20:52,439 --> 00:20:54,406
No. I meant that you need to move on.

286
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:57,520
I'm sorry.

287
00:21:00,866 --> 00:21:03,246
Mary. Please.

288
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:06,350
Tim! Tim!

289
00:21:08,740 --> 00:21:09,980
I found it.

290
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:12,526
Fashion heaven is real.

291
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:15,613
I got something for you, too.

292
00:21:17,213 --> 00:21:18,226
Oh, nice!

293
00:21:20,413 --> 00:21:23,719
It's so beautiful. It's... magical.

294
00:21:24,593 --> 00:21:25,819
Fashion heaven.

295
00:21:26,863 --> 00:21:28,159
Can I get out now?

296
00:21:58,340 --> 00:22:01,490
Guys, the hunger strike is over.

297
00:22:02,002 --> 00:22:03,406
Well done.

298
00:22:07,410 --> 00:22:08,846
Could you imagine....

299
00:22:10,106 --> 00:22:11,960
those poor, poor Africans.

